text: Grönlund is a Finnish surname and may refer to: * Ernst Grönlund (1902–1968), Finnish football and bandy player * Timo Grönlund (born 1954), Finnish sprint canoer * Tommi Grönlund (born 1969), Finnish football player * Tommi Grönlund (artist) (born 1967), Finnish artist and label owner (Sähkö Recordings)
title: Grönlund
